{"tid":2426378,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黃子悅: 「山中人自正，路險心亦平」感謝大家關心","createTime":"2021-02-28T05:17:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-01T02:49:08.000Z","uid":240362,"like":92,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"6d45e0ff606f6012959fc7b8ebfcefb28698adcd","tid":2426378,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T05:17:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-hkt1-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/154580617_260122005552422_9173833890524057670_n.jpg?_nc_cat=106&amp;ccb=3&amp;_nc_sid=8bfeb9&amp;_nc_ohc=hiwEbTGIYL8AX-79lxz&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkt1-2.xx&amp;oh=b81234aed69d040c1817261ea7dac188&amp;oe=60624C18\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkt1-2.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F154580617_260122005552422_9173833890524057670_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D106%26ccb%3D3%26_nc_sid%3D8bfeb9%26_nc_ohc%3DhiwEbTGIYL8AX-79lxz%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkt1-2.xx%26oh%3Db81234aed69d040c1817261ea7dac188%26oe%3D60624C18&h=d39c0bd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「若然」<br />\n<br />\n正值大學最後一個sem，本來想着還有兩三個月終於可以畢業。有了新的背囊，想着可以走遍香港的山野。還想儲錢買一架公路單車。還想跟所愛之人牽手走過每天，想可以快點畢業給家用。<br />\n<br />\n原本這個限期是兩三年後的暴動案審訊。結果限期可能提早，太突然，仍然沒有實感。<br />\n<br />\n就像發噩夢。小時候我每晚都會發噩夢，總會害怕自己一個睡覺。那種恐怖感仍然深刻。如果明天無力反抗極權的壓迫，就好好修行，希望有天成為內心找到平靜的人。<br />\n<br />\n仍然會怕會哭，但那是因為我擁有很多，很幸福，所以才不捨、難受。<br />\n<br />\n山中人自正，路險心亦平。感謝大家的關心，假如真的還押，希望當我出來的時候，大家還在，還在堅持着。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/wongjiyuet97/photos/a.119810819583542/260122002219089/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwongjiyuet97%2Fphotos%2Fa.119810819583542%2F260122002219089%2F&d=zAz8RNAQ9Ot7v23HNjWT3rO6ciNacqKxYXGqE8pVUEM%3D&h=f983c398\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/wongjiyuet97/photos/a.119810819583542/260122002219089/</a>"},{"pid":"36cdfafe1d4401eebd9ed43937298a8c25c6addd","tid":2426378,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T05:20:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kil